@startuml cli_mode_structure

title __main__.py Module Structure: CLI and Interactive Modes

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

class "cli_mode()" as CliMode <<entry point>> {
    + cli_mode() : None
}

class "_parse_cli_arguments()" as ParseArgs {
    - _parse_cli_arguments(registry: dict) : tuple | None
}

class "_execute_cli_mode()" as ExecuteCli {
    - _execute_cli_mode(operation: str,\n  operands: list, registry: dict) : None
}

class "_run_interactive_loop()" as InteractiveLoop {
    - _run_interactive_loop(registry: dict) : None
}

class "_build_registry()" as BuildRegistry {
    - _build_registry(calculator: Calculator) : dict
}

class "_parse_number()" as ParseNumber {
    - _parse_number(raw: str) : int | float
}

class "main()" as LegacyMain <<legacy>> {
    + main() : None
}

class "Calculator" as Calc {
    .. Binary Arithmetic ..
    + add(a, b) : int|float
    + subtract(a, b) : int|float
    + multiply(a, b) : int|float
    + divide(a, b) : float
    + power(base, exponent) : int|float
    .. Unary Operations ..
    + factorial(n) : int
    + square(x) : int|float
    + cube(x) : int|float
    + square_root(x) : float
    + cube_root(x) : float
    + log10(x) : float
    + ln(x) : float
}

note top of CliMode
  Main dispatcher — invoked by
  the __main__ block at module level
end note

note right of ExecuteCli
  CLI path: resolves registry[operation]
  and calls method(*operands)
end note

note left of InteractiveLoop
  Interactive path: REPL loop,
  calls _parse_number() per operand
end note

note bottom of LegacyMain
  Legacy entry point — creates
  Calculator, builds registry,
  runs interactive loop directly
end note

CliMode --> Calc           : Calculator()
CliMode --> BuildRegistry  : _build_registry(calculator)
CliMode ..> ParseArgs      : _parse_cli_arguments(registry)
CliMode ..> ExecuteCli     : if CLI args present
CliMode ..> InteractiveLoop : fallback if no CLI args

BuildRegistry --> Calc     : depends on instance

ExecuteCli ..> Calc        : registry[op](*operands)

InteractiveLoop ..> ParseNumber : _parse_number(raw)

LegacyMain --> Calc          : Calculator()
LegacyMain --> BuildRegistry  : _build_registry(calculator)
LegacyMain --> InteractiveLoop : _run_interactive_loop(registry)

@enduml
